### Release Notes

<details>
<summary>timonweb/django-tailwind (django-tailwind)</summary>

### [`v4.4.1`](https://redirect.github.com/timonweb/django-tailwind/blob/HEAD/CHANGELOG.md#441)

[Compare Source](https://redirect.github.com/timonweb/django-tailwind/compare/4.4.0...4.4.1)

- Fixes an issue when `raw_input` is used instead of `input`.

### [`v4.4.0`](https://redirect.github.com/timonweb/django-tailwind/blob/HEAD/CHANGELOG.md#440)

[Compare Source](https://redirect.github.com/timonweb/django-tailwind/compare/4.3.1...4.4.0)

- Standalone Tailwind CSS binary support via [pytailwindcss](https://redirect.github.com/timonweb/pytailwindcss);
- `TAILWIND_USE_STANDALONE_BINARY` setting to force standalone binary mode;
- `TAILWIND_STANDALONE_BINARY_VERSION` setting to control standalone binary version (default: `v4.1.16`);
- Automatic detection of standalone vs npm-based installations (checks for `package.json` presence);
- `app_template_v4_standalone/` cookiecutter template for standalone binary apps;
- Updates documentation;
- `Node.js` is now optional when using standalone binary mode;

### [`v4.3.1`](https://redirect.github.com/timonweb/django-tailwind/compare/4.3.0...4.3.1)

[Compare Source](https://redirect.github.com/timonweb/django-tailwind/compare/4.3.0...4.3.1)

### [`v4.3.0`](https://redirect.github.com/timonweb/django-tailwind/blob/HEAD/CHANGELOG.md#430)

[Compare Source](https://redirect.github.com/timonweb/django-tailwind/compare/4.2.0...4.3.0)

- Replaces Poetry with UV for dependency management;
- Fixes `extract_host_and_port` to support standalone port numbers (e.g., `python manage.py runserver 55555`);
- Updates tox configuration to use `dev` dependency group;
- Removes Docker instructions from documentation;

### [`v4.2.0`](https://redirect.github.com/timonweb/django-tailwind/blob/HEAD/CHANGELOG.md#420)

[Compare Source](https://redirect.github.com/timonweb/django-tailwind/compare/4.1.0...4.2.0)

- Adds new `manage.py tailwind plugin_install` command to manage Tailwind CSS plugins;
- Adds optional daisyUI support;

### [`v4.1.0`](https://redirect.github.com/timonweb/django-tailwind/blob/HEAD/CHANGELOG.md#410)

[Compare Source](https://redirect.github.com/timonweb/django-tailwind/compare/4.0.1...4.1.0)

- Adds new `dev` command that starts Django development server and Tailwind watcher simultaneously;
- Automatically installs Honcho if not available when using `dev` command;
- Creates `Procfile.tailwind` for customizable process management;
- Updates documentation with `dev` command usage;

</details>

